00:00:35.370 --> 00:00:54.010 align:middle line:90%


00:00:54.010 --> 00:00:57.370 align:middle line:84%
About five years ago, I
lived on the Rosebud Sioux

00:00:57.370 --> 00:01:01.210 align:middle line:84%
Indian reservation
with my ex-husband,

00:01:01.210 --> 00:01:04.840 align:middle line:90%
and this is my story.

00:01:04.840 --> 00:01:07.630 align:middle line:84%
I'm of French, Mohawk,
and Abenaki descent,

00:01:07.630 --> 00:01:13.700 align:middle line:84%
and I met my ex-husband at
a powwow in Massachusetts,

00:01:13.700 --> 00:01:18.070 align:middle line:84%
married him, and
moved out to Rosebud.

00:01:18.070 --> 00:01:21.460 align:middle line:84%
When I married Jim, I thought
I was marrying a older

00:01:21.460 --> 00:01:24.250 align:middle line:84%
spiritual person, and
I was soon to find out

00:01:24.250 --> 00:01:26.300 align:middle line:90%
that wasn't the case.

00:01:26.300 --> 00:01:30.770 align:middle line:84%
I spent almost two
years of physical abuse.

00:01:30.770 --> 00:01:33.520 align:middle line:84%
The abuse was so severe
that he would tell me

00:01:33.520 --> 00:01:35.860 align:middle line:90%
when I could answer questions.

00:01:35.860 --> 00:01:41.080 align:middle line:84%
He basically destroyed
any past life experience--

00:01:41.080 --> 00:01:43.270 align:middle line:90%
you know, my families--

00:01:43.270 --> 00:01:46.870 align:middle line:84%
and he tried to kill
me several times.

00:01:46.870 --> 00:01:53.500 align:middle line:84%
And my saving grace was
the Lakota religion.

00:01:53.500 --> 00:01:58.640 align:middle line:84%
His brother, Florentine, one
night went to go to ceremony.

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:00.940 align:middle line:90%
He's a medicine man.

00:02:00.940 --> 00:02:03.880 align:middle line:84%
And I had two children
with me at the time.

00:02:03.880 --> 00:02:06.550 align:middle line:84%
And my children and I
couldn't go to the ceremony,

00:02:06.550 --> 00:02:10.930 align:middle line:84%
but Florentine said that
everybody would pray for us.

00:02:10.930 --> 00:02:15.460 align:middle line:84%
And about 3 o'clock
in the morning,

00:02:15.460 --> 00:02:19.900 align:middle line:84%
I was laying on the couch,
and I heard the door open.

00:02:19.900 --> 00:02:22.690 align:middle line:84%
And I looked and
the door was closed.

00:02:22.690 --> 00:02:24.560 align:middle line:90%
And then I looked at the clock.

00:02:24.560 --> 00:02:27.010 align:middle line:90%
It was 3:01.

00:02:27.010 --> 00:02:32.200 align:middle line:84%
And I felt the circle of
cold air blowing my face,

00:02:32.200 --> 00:02:34.980 align:middle line:84%
and I was very scared, so
scared that I couldn't yell

00:02:34.980 --> 00:02:35.780 align:middle line:90%
or anything.

00:02:35.780 --> 00:02:38.860 align:middle line:84%
And there was no one
there except my children.

00:02:38.860 --> 00:02:40.540 align:middle line:90%
And my hair was blowing back.

00:02:40.540 --> 00:02:44.140 align:middle line:84%
And then I felt like someone's
warm hand touched my head,

00:02:44.140 --> 00:02:47.320 align:middle line:84%
and I felt warm all the
way down to my feet.

00:02:47.320 --> 00:02:50.530 align:middle line:84%
And then a voice
inside my head said,

00:02:50.530 --> 00:02:54.210 align:middle line:84%
Jim will go back to where he
came from, and you will be OK,

00:02:54.210 --> 00:02:55.930 align:middle line:90%
but you will be hurt some more.

00:02:55.930 --> 00:02:57.970 align:middle line:84%
By the time I woke
up in the morning,

00:02:57.970 --> 00:03:00.220 align:middle line:84%
I thought that I had
imagined the whole thing.

00:03:00.220 --> 00:03:03.760 align:middle line:84%
Florentine came home
about 7 o'clock,

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:05.420 align:middle line:90%
and I went to greet him.

00:03:05.420 --> 00:03:08.550 align:middle line:84%
And he took my hair, and
he said, what happened?

00:03:08.550 --> 00:03:11.380 align:middle line:84%
It looks like you rode
in the back of a pickup.

00:03:11.380 --> 00:03:15.310 align:middle line:84%
And then I realized that
I hadn't dreamt that.

00:03:15.310 --> 00:03:18.220 align:middle line:84%
And he said, a lot of
people pray for you tonight.

00:03:18.220 --> 00:03:21.850 align:middle line:84%
And about 3 o'clock, Elmer
sent the spirits out to check

00:03:21.850 --> 00:03:23.320 align:middle line:84%
on the people that
were prayed for.

00:03:23.320 --> 00:03:25.310 align:middle line:90%
Did you notice anything?

00:03:25.310 --> 00:03:28.660 align:middle line:84%
And that was kind of when
my life turned around,

00:03:28.660 --> 00:03:32.340 align:middle line:84%
when I believed that there
was a spiritual world.

00:03:32.340 --> 00:03:35.790 align:middle line:90%


00:03:35.790 --> 00:03:39.770 align:middle line:84%
The abuse continued, but right
before his big plan to kill me,

00:03:39.770 --> 00:03:41.780 align:middle line:90%
the federal agents came in.

00:03:41.780 --> 00:03:46.010 align:middle line:84%
He was hauled off to
prison, and I found out

00:03:46.010 --> 00:03:48.120 align:middle line:84%
that he had spent
17 years in prison.

00:03:48.120 --> 00:03:50.180 align:middle line:84%
So, in essence, the
spirits were right

00:03:50.180 --> 00:03:52.910 align:middle line:84%
that he did go back
to where he came from.

00:03:52.910 --> 00:03:54.740 align:middle line:84%
He came from
prison, and now he's

00:03:54.740 --> 00:03:58.110 align:middle line:90%
in a federal prison for life.

00:03:58.110 --> 00:03:59.960 align:middle line:84%
I knew that he
served time, but what

00:03:59.960 --> 00:04:04.220 align:middle line:84%
I was told by the New
Hampshire parole commission

00:04:04.220 --> 00:04:06.080 align:middle line:90%
was that he was framed.

00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:09.590 align:middle line:84%
And Jim said that he
never killed anybody,

00:04:09.590 --> 00:04:13.350 align:middle line:90%
and I believe that to be true.

00:04:13.350 --> 00:04:17.529 align:middle line:84%
I couldn't believe that someone
could commit the brutal murder

00:04:17.529 --> 00:04:18.329 align:middle line:90%
that he did.

00:04:18.329 --> 00:04:20.930 align:middle line:84%
But after they hauled
him off to Sioux Falls,

00:04:20.930 --> 00:04:25.350 align:middle line:84%
I was actually able to go
in and read that whole case.

00:04:25.350 --> 00:04:27.680 align:middle line:84%
And there were
family witnesses that

00:04:27.680 --> 00:04:33.890 align:middle line:84%
came through to verify that they
saw him murder his first wife.

00:04:33.890 --> 00:04:38.840 align:middle line:84%
From that point on, the
Lakota women and medicine man

00:04:38.840 --> 00:04:41.210 align:middle line:84%
and his wife on the
reservation helped me

00:04:41.210 --> 00:04:44.810 align:middle line:84%
with my own spiritual
healing, because I have

00:04:44.810 --> 00:04:46.800 align:middle line:90%
post-traumatic stress disorder.

00:04:46.800 --> 00:04:49.450 align:middle line:90%
[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

00:04:49.450 --> 00:04:58.210 align:middle line:84%
I have nightmares of one time
Jim grabbed the back of my head

00:04:58.210 --> 00:05:01.840 align:middle line:84%
and threw my head
through a glass table.

00:05:01.840 --> 00:05:05.950 align:middle line:84%
And I don't know
what triggers it,

00:05:05.950 --> 00:05:08.480 align:middle line:84%
but it's getting better
as the years pass.

00:05:08.480 --> 00:05:13.600 align:middle line:84%
And I was lucky that I was
given a pipe to pray with.

00:05:13.600 --> 00:05:18.460 align:middle line:84%
And I pray for healing, and
I also pray for clarity.

00:05:18.460 --> 00:05:20.850 align:middle line:84%
And one of the
things, when I pray, I

00:05:20.850 --> 00:05:23.590 align:middle line:84%
say [SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]
and that's

00:05:23.590 --> 00:05:29.460 align:middle line:84%
like please give me
clarity and understanding.

00:05:29.460 --> 00:05:32.670 align:middle line:84%
I was given a
chanunpa to pray with,

00:05:32.670 --> 00:05:34.480 align:middle line:90%
and life is really good now.

00:05:34.480 --> 00:05:37.740 align:middle line:84%
I moved back home, but
I pray with my pipe.

00:05:37.740 --> 00:05:39.510 align:middle line:84%
And I still remember
those connections

00:05:39.510 --> 00:05:40.690 align:middle line:90%
with the Lakota people.

00:05:40.690 --> 00:05:42.510 align:middle line:90%
And that's how I worship now.

00:05:42.510 --> 00:05:44.230 align:middle line:84%
I think this story
is good too tell

00:05:44.230 --> 00:05:47.340 align:middle line:84%
for women who are
in a situation,

00:05:47.340 --> 00:05:51.120 align:middle line:84%
that you can pray and
get through anything.

00:05:51.120 --> 00:05:55.610 align:middle line:84%
And I truly believe in calling
in the spirits of the four

00:05:55.610 --> 00:05:58.225 align:middle line:84%
direction and getting those
spirits or angels, whatever

00:05:58.225 --> 00:05:59.850 align:middle line:84%
you want to call
them, to work for you.

00:05:59.850 --> 00:06:03.340 align:middle line:90%


00:06:03.340 --> 00:06:07.090 align:middle line:84%
Back five or six years ago,
I was a naive little girl

00:06:07.090 --> 00:06:10.090 align:middle line:84%
from Vermont and couldn't
imagine anybody ever killing

00:06:10.090 --> 00:06:11.620 align:middle line:90%
anybody.

00:06:11.620 --> 00:06:15.240 align:middle line:84%
And I was very linear
in my thinking.

00:06:15.240 --> 00:06:17.030 align:middle line:84%
I didn't believe
in a spirit world.

00:06:17.030 --> 00:06:19.240 align:middle line:90%
I didn't believe in angels.

00:06:19.240 --> 00:06:21.810 align:middle line:84%
And after my experiences
on the Rosebud

00:06:21.810 --> 00:06:26.320 align:middle line:84%
and the continued experiences
in my own spirituality,

00:06:26.320 --> 00:06:28.750 align:middle line:84%
I know that there are
angels or spirits, however

00:06:28.750 --> 00:06:31.690 align:middle line:84%
way you want to say it, that
look over me and are beside me.

00:06:31.690 --> 00:06:35.410 align:middle line:84%
And that you can call
on them to help you when

00:06:35.410 --> 00:06:38.102 align:middle line:90%
you're feeling really weak.

00:06:38.102 --> 00:06:40.840 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:06:40.840 --> 00:06:45.040 align:middle line:84%
And I also know that if it
wasn't for the angels and all

00:06:45.040 --> 00:06:46.930 align:middle line:84%
the prayers of
the Lakota people,

00:06:46.930 --> 00:06:51.380 align:middle line:84%
I wouldn't be on my
healing journey now.

00:06:51.380 --> 00:06:54.248 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:06:54.248 --> 00:06:57.120 align:middle line:90%


00:06:57.120 --> 00:06:59.940 align:middle line:84%
>> When I was little, the way
I would see things was a bit

00:06:59.940 --> 00:07:01.350 align:middle line:90%
different than other people.

00:07:01.350 --> 00:07:04.260 align:middle line:84%
I would see auras
around people, which

00:07:04.260 --> 00:07:05.560 align:middle line:90%
I didn't know what that was.

00:07:05.560 --> 00:07:10.120 align:middle line:84%
But I thought that everyone
saw people glowing.

00:07:10.120 --> 00:07:12.450 align:middle line:84%
You know, I'd walk into the
room, and everybody glowed.

00:07:12.450 --> 00:07:15.210 align:middle line:84%
Or if someone was angry
or having a fight,

00:07:15.210 --> 00:07:18.250 align:middle line:84%
I would see a mass of energy
going through the room.

00:07:18.250 --> 00:07:21.090 align:middle line:90%
And I can remember feeling--

00:07:21.090 --> 00:07:24.480 align:middle line:84%
when I would see these things,
I thought, oh, my god, it's

00:07:24.480 --> 00:07:25.710 align:middle line:90%
an evil spirit or something.

00:07:25.710 --> 00:07:28.920 align:middle line:84%
Because I was brought up in
a very severely Catholic kind

00:07:28.920 --> 00:07:31.740 align:middle line:84%
of family, where we did
the rosary every night,

00:07:31.740 --> 00:07:35.400 align:middle line:84%
church every day, and it was
the major monster God scene.

00:07:35.400 --> 00:07:39.330 align:middle line:90%
So I really felt--

00:07:39.330 --> 00:07:43.140 align:middle line:84%
I would say I felt terrified
most of my life, just terrified

00:07:43.140 --> 00:07:47.392 align:middle line:90%
of everything.

00:07:47.392 --> 00:07:50.640 align:middle line:90%
[RHYTHMIC DRUMMING]

00:07:50.640 --> 00:07:54.240 align:middle line:84%
What I was perceiving,
other people weren't.

00:07:54.240 --> 00:07:57.240 align:middle line:84%
And so there was no
map for me to follow.

00:07:57.240 --> 00:08:00.330 align:middle line:84%
There was no one for
me to reflect off

00:08:00.330 --> 00:08:02.850 align:middle line:90%
to or feel supported by.

00:08:02.850 --> 00:08:05.745 align:middle line:84%
And so that left knee in
that place of feeling alone.

00:08:05.745 --> 00:08:09.680 align:middle line:90%


00:08:09.680 --> 00:08:12.450 align:middle line:84%
I became very quiet
for a while, until I

00:08:12.450 --> 00:08:15.624 align:middle line:84%
started to tell more about
what I was seeing still,

00:08:15.624 --> 00:08:16.665 align:middle line:90%
because it never stopped.

00:08:16.665 --> 00:08:19.260 align:middle line:90%


00:08:19.260 --> 00:08:24.830 align:middle line:84%
I had an experience going to a
very orthodox religious church,

00:08:24.830 --> 00:08:27.180 align:middle line:90%
and they said I was evil.

00:08:27.180 --> 00:08:28.860 align:middle line:84%
They said I shouldn't
know what I know.

00:08:28.860 --> 00:08:31.350 align:middle line:84%
They said I shouldn't
see what I see.

00:08:31.350 --> 00:08:33.360 align:middle line:90%
So I closed down more.

00:08:33.360 --> 00:08:35.220 align:middle line:84%
They brought me to the
medical profession.

00:08:35.220 --> 00:08:40.930 align:middle line:84%
The medical profession said,
well, let's do CAT scans.

00:08:40.930 --> 00:08:41.730 align:middle line:90%
Let's shoot dye.

00:08:41.730 --> 00:08:43.409 align:middle line:90%
Let's see if we can find tumors.

00:08:43.409 --> 00:08:44.510 align:middle line:90%
Let's look.

00:08:44.510 --> 00:08:47.070 align:middle line:90%
So it was test, test, test.

00:08:47.070 --> 00:08:50.490 align:middle line:84%
You know, I started to feel more
and more just like an object,

00:08:50.490 --> 00:08:52.770 align:middle line:90%
that I didn't belong.

00:08:52.770 --> 00:08:55.782 align:middle line:84%
I was, I could just
say, terrified.

00:08:55.782 --> 00:08:58.578 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:08:58.578 --> 00:08:59.980 align:middle line:90%


00:08:59.980 --> 00:09:01.900 align:middle line:84%
So they sent me
to the psych ward.

00:09:01.900 --> 00:09:04.540 align:middle line:84%
And then once at the psych ward,
they didn't know what to do,

00:09:04.540 --> 00:09:08.069 align:middle line:84%
because I did a great job on the
block test, on all the tests.

00:09:08.069 --> 00:09:10.360 align:middle line:84%
And they couldn't quite get
it, but they thought, well,

00:09:10.360 --> 00:09:12.640 align:middle line:90%
maybe let's give her some--

00:09:12.640 --> 00:09:15.970 align:middle line:90%
you know, put her on something.

00:09:15.970 --> 00:09:18.610 align:middle line:84%
So they started putting
labels on me there.

00:09:18.610 --> 00:09:23.320 align:middle line:84%
And so I started to
sort of believe it.

00:09:23.320 --> 00:09:25.780 align:middle line:84%
I also thought,
well, if what I'm

00:09:25.780 --> 00:09:28.960 align:middle line:84%
seeing is really true, if I'm
really seeing people glow,

00:09:28.960 --> 00:09:32.710 align:middle line:84%
if I'm seeing thought forms,
I'm seeing like little entity

00:09:32.710 --> 00:09:36.310 align:middle line:84%
things at different times,
I was preferring there

00:09:36.310 --> 00:09:37.660 align:middle line:90%
be something wrong with me.

00:09:37.660 --> 00:09:39.451 align:middle line:84%
Because then, at least,
I fit in somewhere.

00:09:39.451 --> 00:09:42.290 align:middle line:90%
I had a label that fit.

00:09:42.290 --> 00:09:49.830 align:middle line:84%
When I was 15, my sisters,
two of my sisters, drowned.

00:09:49.830 --> 00:09:51.500 align:middle line:90%
It was my younger sister.

00:09:51.500 --> 00:09:52.760 align:middle line:90%
She was nine.

00:09:52.760 --> 00:09:57.230 align:middle line:84%
And then my older
sister, who was--

00:09:57.230 --> 00:09:59.810 align:middle line:90%
she was about 21.

00:09:59.810 --> 00:10:02.450 align:middle line:90%
And we had gone to Sicily.

00:10:02.450 --> 00:10:04.700 align:middle line:84%
It was our whole family,
except for my father

00:10:04.700 --> 00:10:08.120 align:middle line:84%
and another sister who
lives in Guatemala.

00:10:08.120 --> 00:10:11.900 align:middle line:84%
So we went to Sicily to
visit, and we were going down

00:10:11.900 --> 00:10:15.230 align:middle line:84%
to the ocean to swim, because we
were all really good swimmers.

00:10:15.230 --> 00:10:18.330 align:middle line:90%
And I had a feeling.

00:10:18.330 --> 00:10:21.530 align:middle line:84%
Something said, you know,
I'd rather stay on dry land.

00:10:21.530 --> 00:10:24.970 align:middle line:90%
I just had those senses, anyway.

00:10:24.970 --> 00:10:27.870 align:middle line:84%
But we went down,
and we went swimming.

00:10:27.870 --> 00:10:30.260 align:middle line:84%
My little sister was
walking along the beach,

00:10:30.260 --> 00:10:32.450 align:middle line:90%
and the undertow took her out.

00:10:32.450 --> 00:10:35.690 align:middle line:90%
My older sister went in.

00:10:35.690 --> 00:10:40.340 align:middle line:84%
And myself and my two brothers
went in and got shot out again.

00:10:40.340 --> 00:10:43.250 align:middle line:84%
And then, by this time,
other people grabbed us.

00:10:43.250 --> 00:10:45.590 align:middle line:84%
And so it was my sister,
my little sister,

00:10:45.590 --> 00:10:48.380 align:middle line:90%
out there and my older sister.

00:10:48.380 --> 00:10:50.600 align:middle line:90%
My sisters drowned.

00:10:50.600 --> 00:10:53.840 align:middle line:84%
I couldn't do
anything, just watched.

00:10:53.840 --> 00:10:59.120 align:middle line:84%
And at that point, it was a real
powerful turning point for me

00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:02.220 align:middle line:90%
at that time.

00:11:02.220 --> 00:11:06.800 align:middle line:84%
That was the time I
decided I wanted to live.

00:11:06.800 --> 00:11:09.140 align:middle line:84%
Because before
that, I was between.

00:11:09.140 --> 00:11:12.290 align:middle line:84%
And I think that's a
lot about why I fought

00:11:12.290 --> 00:11:14.530 align:middle line:90%
inside myself to keep going.

00:11:14.530 --> 00:11:19.790 align:middle line:10%
Because in what happened
with them and their deaths,

00:11:19.790 --> 00:11:22.400 align:middle line:10%
somehow it clicked,
and I want to live.

00:11:22.400 --> 00:11:24.190 align:middle line:90%
And I kept going.

00:11:24.190 --> 00:11:26.420 align:middle line:90%
[RHYTHMIC DRUMMING]

00:11:26.420 --> 00:11:31.700 align:middle line:84%
And finally, a brochure came
do the math for Barbara Brennan

00:11:31.700 --> 00:11:34.010 align:middle line:90%
and Pat Rodegast in Phoenix.

00:11:34.010 --> 00:11:35.704 align:middle line:90%
And I had no idea who they were.

00:11:35.704 --> 00:11:37.370 align:middle line:84%
I didn't know what
that world was about.

00:11:37.370 --> 00:11:41.060 align:middle line:84%
But something, the impulse
inside, said, you have to go.

00:11:41.060 --> 00:11:41.940 align:middle line:90%
You have to go.

00:11:41.940 --> 00:11:43.760 align:middle line:90%
And so I did.

00:11:43.760 --> 00:11:48.230 align:middle line:84%
And at this point, what
I did was meet Barbara,

00:11:48.230 --> 00:11:50.580 align:middle line:90%
and she told me her story.

00:11:50.580 --> 00:11:52.880 align:middle line:84%
She let me know I was
psychic, I was clairvoyant,

00:11:52.880 --> 00:11:54.710 align:middle line:90%
I wasn't crazy.

00:11:54.710 --> 00:12:00.540 align:middle line:84%
And so that that's where my
world started to shift around.

00:12:00.540 --> 00:12:02.520 align:middle line:84%
I studied with her
for four years.

00:12:02.520 --> 00:12:05.210 align:middle line:84%
And it's really the time I
call my nervous breakthrough,

00:12:05.210 --> 00:12:08.930 align:middle line:84%
because it's where everything,
all sense of who I thought I

00:12:08.930 --> 00:12:11.780 align:middle line:84%
was, who they told
me I was, I wasn't.

00:12:11.780 --> 00:12:15.180 align:middle line:90%


00:12:15.180 --> 00:12:18.960 align:middle line:84%
What I do now is I work
as an energy therapist.

00:12:18.960 --> 00:12:21.960 align:middle line:84%
I used to dance
professionally, so I

00:12:21.960 --> 00:12:24.690 align:middle line:84%
take the movement and the energy
work and I put that together

00:12:24.690 --> 00:12:27.900 align:middle line:84%
and teach channeling
classes, which is just

00:12:27.900 --> 00:12:30.210 align:middle line:84%
about getting people in
touch with their inner knower

00:12:30.210 --> 00:12:32.640 align:middle line:84%
and, actually, just
their god selves.

00:12:32.640 --> 00:12:34.290 align:middle line:84%
And just remembering
who they are

00:12:34.290 --> 00:12:38.520 align:middle line:84%
and just having that sense
of empowerment in the world.

00:12:38.520 --> 00:12:41.400 align:middle line:84%
I never thought I'd ever
be doing what I'm doing.

00:12:41.400 --> 00:12:44.070 align:middle line:90%
It was not in the plans.

00:12:44.070 --> 00:12:45.814 align:middle line:84%
When I was little,
I never thought, oh,

00:12:45.814 --> 00:12:46.980 align:middle line:90%
that's what I'm going to do.

00:12:46.980 --> 00:12:47.880 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to grow
up, and I'm going

00:12:47.880 --> 00:12:50.490 align:middle line:84%
to be a healer and work with
energy and that kind of thing.

00:12:50.490 --> 00:12:53.330 align:middle line:90%


00:12:53.330 --> 00:12:57.920 align:middle line:84%
I was sort of in this abyss,
and I had to restructure myself.

00:12:57.920 --> 00:13:01.110 align:middle line:84%
And still, I'm still
doing it, you know.

00:13:01.110 --> 00:13:04.940 align:middle line:90%
It's like a good 20 years later.

00:13:04.940 --> 00:13:07.340 align:middle line:84%
And I hope that I
keep restructuring

00:13:07.340 --> 00:13:10.760 align:middle line:84%
that, I keep remaining
fluid enough to do that.

00:13:10.760 --> 00:13:15.610 align:middle line:90%


00:13:15.610 --> 00:13:18.520 align:middle line:90%
